{"word":"G4510 - ῥυπόω - rhypóō - rhoo-po'-o - Be filthy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥυπόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">rhypóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">rhoo-po'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be filthy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அசுத்தமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to make filthy, defile, soil"},{"paragraph":"2. to be filthy: morally"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4509 - ῥύπος - rhýpos - hroo'-pos/4509\">G4509</a>; to <i>soil</i>, that is, (intransitively) to <i>become dirty</i> (morally): - be filthy.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}